version_description:
iOS7 design and compatibility.
New functions to create new calc, save and load state. It is now possible to backup the actual state of calc.
Corrected binary header for Save Object...
Keypad improvement for iPhone 5 skin.
Users documents and data are now synchronized to iCloud.
Bug fixes.

- Display enhancement
- Keyboard speed enhancement
- Web server port changed to avoid conflict with other applications
- Compatibility with latest iOS 10
